--- LaTeX table (paste into manuscript) ---

\begin{table}[t]
  \caption{ToolBench retrieval under three category-tag conditions (BGE-base backend, 1100 queries, $k = 5$, 95\% bootstrap CIs). The ``oracle'' condition uses the benchmark's ground-truth category labels as \texttt{required\_tags} (the original manuscript condition). The ``LLM-inferred (top-5)'' condition asks claude-sonnet-4-6 to return the top 5 ranked categories from the closed vocabulary, with no access to ground-truth labels (set-level accuracy = 0.848, mean set size = 5.00 after dedup, hard-capped at 5). The ``no governance'' condition strips all scope metadata.}
